      "cookedHtml": "<p>Imagine a world where you never miss a beat on your interested YouTube channel! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Thanks to the magic of <a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a>, I’ve set up a mind-blowing scenario that turns every new comment into an organized masterpiece for any Youtube channel that you prefer! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/man_mage.png?v=12\" title=\":man_mage:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":man_mage:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=12\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Watch for New Comments:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Activate the magic with the “Watch New Comment of Any YouTube Channels” spell. Now, your system keeps an eye out for any fresh comments on your YouTube videos. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/man_mage.png?v=12\" title=\":man_mage:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":man_mage:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eye.png?v=12\" title=\":eye:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eye:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Find the Video Link:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>When a new comment appears, the system automatically searches for the video link using the “Search” wand from <a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a>. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/man_detective.png?v=12\" title=\":man_detective:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":man_detective:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_with_meridians.png?v=12\" title=\":globe_with_meridians:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_with_meridians:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Create a Subitem Spell:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>With the video link in hand, a new comment is conjured as a neat subitem, seamlessly attaching itself to the video. No more chaos, just organized comments! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/magic_wand.png?v=12\" title=\":magic_wand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":magic_wand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Let the Magic Unfold:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Sit back and enjoy as your YouTube comments transform into an orderly collection of subitems. The whole process is automated, leaving you with more time for the things you love! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tea.png?v=12\" title=\":tea:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tea:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/relieved.png?v=12\" title=\":relieved:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":relieved:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Share the Easy Magic:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Spread the word about this enchanting automation. Your community will love the simplicity of turning comments into neatly organized content. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/loudspeaker.png?v=12\" title=\":loudspeaker:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":loudspeaker:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Welcome to the world of easy YouTube comment management, thanks to the simplicity of <a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a>! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rainbow.png?v=12\" title=\":rainbow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rainbow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/4/241128ca964c50ac75e75c26b457a93a6b0a4824.png\" title=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (20)\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/4/241128ca964c50ac75e75c26b457a93a6b0a4824_2_690x270.png\" alt=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (20)\" width=\"690\" height=\"270\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">MicrosoftTeams-image (20)</span><span class=\"informations\">1020×400 22.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/a/fa214369182bfc6b16e20fb2f2cbf23e85068de5.png\" title=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (21)\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/a/fa214369182bfc6b16e20fb2f2cbf23e85068de5_2_690x342.png\" alt=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (21)\" width=\"690\" height=\"342\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">MicrosoftTeams-image (21)</span><span class=\"info